data.description: This is a fantastic opportunity to own your own home that you can live in while you complete the updates you desire.  Loads of room for all, this well built home awaits its new owner.  This home is located on the south side of Georgetown on a partially wooded lot with a circular driveway and partially fenced back yard.  There is so much potential for sweat equity.   There is a new heat pump and newer water heater.  There are real hardwood floors throughout the home, along with a double sided fireplace between the huge living room and the secluded family room.  A formal dining room awaits all of your festive dinners and guests, along with an enclosed porch that could be used as an office, and a well laid out kitchen.  This is a short sale, but should be able to close in a reasonable amount of time.  This listing price is a bank approved short sale sales price.
